                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8730" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1336</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2395 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">好水养好鱼——观星农业的数字化水质风险防控之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Good Water for Raising Fish--Digital Water Quality Risk Prevention and Control of Guanxing Agriculture</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘端，刘慧宇，潘聪，谢骏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州观星农业科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化；风险识别、评估、控制；价值链；生产活动；2024百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digitization; Risk identification, assessment, and management; Value chain; Production activity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在“着力创新智慧渔业模式”的新发展环境中，养殖企业开始基于自身价值链思考如何利用数字化在关键贡献环节进行风险控制，以改善产品质量，保障企业市场竞争力。本案例以观星农业的生产环节风险管理为主线，描述了企业在生产活动中的数字化风险防控过程。观星农业进行生产管理风险识别和评估之后，聚焦于核心的水质风险点，着手数字化改革，建立全流程全方位水环境数字化监测系统和数字化预警—报警机制，改善了生态池塘和生产养殖箱的水质，解决了生产活动的主要风险问题。最终企业提升了水产品品质，增强了品牌效应和议价能力。本案例旨在帮助学员了解风险管理的相关理论，理解水产养殖企业如何利用数字化技术进行风险防控，对农业企业利用数字化加强风险控制有一定的借鉴作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> In the new development environment of “focusing on innovation of smart fishery model”, aquaculture enterprises are exploring how to use digital technology for risk control in key contribution links based on their own value chain, to improve product quality and ensure market competitiveness. This case study focuses on the risk management of Guanxing Agriculture in production activities and describes the process of digital risk prevention and control. After conducting risk identification and assessment, Guanxing Agriculture focused on water quality risk, initiated digital transformation, established a comprehensive digital monitoring system for water environment and an early-warning mechanism, improved the water quality of ecological ponds and production and breeding tanks, and solved the main risk problems of production activities. As a result, the enterprise improved the quality of aquatic products and thus enhanced the brand effect and bargaining power. This case study aims to help students gain an in-depth understanding of the relevant theories of risk management, understand how aquaculture enterprises use digital technology for risk prevention and control, and provide reference for agricultural enterprises to strengthen risk control through digital technology.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业价值链理论；风险识别和评估；风险控制过程；风险控制方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
